\u201313 Eredivisie|2012\u201313]]||23||0||-||-||-||-||8||0||31||0\n|-\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Total\n! colspan=2 | Netherlands\n!313||41||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||52||3||359||44\n|-\n! colspan=2 | England\n!83||1||3||0||2||0||2||0||90||1\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Career total\n!411||42||5||0||2||0||54||3||472||45\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 19 June 2004 || [[Est\u00e1dio Municipal de Aveiro|Est\u00e1dio Municipal]], [[Aveiro, Portugal]] || {{fb|CZE}} || <center>1\u20130</center> || <center>2\u20133</center> || [[Euro 2004]]\n|-\n| 2. || 10 October 2004 || [[Skopje City Stadium|City Stadium]], [[Skopje]], [[Macedonia (country)|Macedonia]] || {{fb|Macedonia}} || <center>0\u20131</center> || <center>2\u20132</center> || [[2006 FIFA World Cup qualification|2006 World Cup qualification]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''PSV Eindhoven'''\n*[[Eredivisie]]: Winner 2000, 2001, 2003, 2005\n*[[KNVB Cup]]: Winner 1996, 2005, 2012\n*[[Johan Cruijff-schaal]]: Winner 2000, 2001, 2003, 2012\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Wilfred Bouma}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n*{{wvo|1122|Wilfred Bouma}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063356/http://www.onsoranje.nl/team-statistieken/teams/speler/11/50a3c201-cd71c692-797849 Netherlands profile] at OnsOranje\n\n{{Navboxes colour\n|bg= #F1771D\n|fg= white\n|title= Netherlands squads\n|list1=\n{{Netherlands Squad UEFA Euro 2004}}\n{{Netherlands Squad 2008 Euro Cup}}\n{{Netherlands squad UEFA Euro 2012}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bouma, Wilfred}}\n[[Category:1978 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Helmond]]\n[[Category:Dutch footballers]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Dutch people of Surinamese descent]]\n[[Category:Netherlands youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Netherlands under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Netherlands international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:PSV Eindhoven players]]\n[[Category:MVV Maastricht players]]\n[[Category:Fortuna Sittard players]]\n[[Category:Aston Villa F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Eredivisie players]]\n[[Category:Eerste Divisie players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2004 players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2008 players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2012 players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in England]]\n[[Category:Dutch expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eInternational career:Typo fixing, replaced: 78th substitute \u2192 78th-minute substitute", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilfred_Bouma"}
