220 |title=Community Mitigation Guidelines to Prevent Pandemic Influenza\u2014United States, 2017 |journal=Recommendations and Reports |volume=66 |issue=1 |date=12 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ImpCollege16mar2020\">{{cite article |title=Impact of non-pharmaceutical interventions (NPIs) to reduce COVID19 mortality and healthcare demand |date=16 March 2020 |work=[[Imperial College]] COVID-19 Response Team |url=https://www.imperial.ac.uk/media/imperial-college/medicine/sph/ide/gida-fellowships/Imperial-College-COVID19-NPI-modelling-16-03-2020.pdf}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"patientZero\">{{cite news |last=Duarte |first=Fernando |title=As the cases of coronavirus increase in China and around the world, the hunt is on to identify \"patient zero\". |work=BBC News |date=24 February 2020 |url=https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20200221-coronavirus-the-harmful-hunt-for-covid-19s-patient-zero | access-date = 22 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WHO report 28 February 2020\">{{cite web |url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/who-china-joint-mission-on-covid-19-final-report.pdf |title=Report of the WHO-China Joint Mission on Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) |date=16\u201324 February 2020 |access-date=8 March 2020 |author=WHO\u2013China Joint Mission |work=[[World Health Organization]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-67\">{{Cite journal |last=Cohen |first=Jon |date=January 2020 |title=Wuhan seafood market may not be source of novel virus spreading globally |url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2020/01/wuhan-seafood-market-may-not-be-source-novel-virus-spreading-globally |journal=[[Science (journal)|Science]] |doi=10.1126/science.abb0611}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"people's war\">{{cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-02/10/c_138771533.htm |title=Xi stresses winning people's war against novel coronavirus |first=Huanchi |last=Xie |date=20 February 2020 |agency=Xinhua News Agency |quote=Xi Jinping, general secretary of the Communist Party of China Centr