]]\n|list=[[List of Super Bowl lead-out programs|Super Bowl lead-out program]]<br />''The Simpsons''<br />alongside<br />''[[American Dad!]]''<br />[[Super Bowl XXXIX|2005]]\n|next=''[[Grey's Anatomy]]''<br />[[Super Bowl XL|2006]]\n}}\n\n{{The Simpsons|state=uncollapsed}}\n{{The Simpsons episodes}}\n{{Navboxes\n|list1=\n{{Matt Groening}}\n{{Gracie Films}}\n{{Rough Draft Studios}}\n{{Fox Animation}}\n{{FOXNetwork Shows (current and upcoming)}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title= [[List of awards and nominations received by The Simpsons|Awards for ''The Simpsons'']]\n|list1=\n{{Annie Award for Best Animated Television Production}}\n{{EmmyAward AnimationLessThanHour}}\n{{People's Choice Award for Favorite New TV Comedy}}\n{{Saturn Award for Best Network Television Series}}\n{{TCA Award for Outstanding Achievement in Comedy}}\n{{TCA Heritage Award}}\n{{Teen Choice Award for Choice Animated Series}}\n{{WritersGuildofAmericaAnimationScreenplay}}\n}}\n{{Subject bar|book=The Simpsons|portal1=The Simpsons|portal2=Animation|portal3=Comedy|portal4=Cartoon |portal5=Television |portal6=United States |portal7=1980s |portal8=1990s|commons=yes|commons-search=Category:The Simpsons|n=yes|n-search=Category:The Simpsons|wikt=yes|wikt-search=Appendix:The Simpsons|q=yes|d=yes|d-search=Q886}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{Featured article}}\n\n<!--\n Please don't add any categories that have the theme of broadcasters that transmit The Simpsons.\n There are too many of these around the world and listing them would clutter the bottom of the page.\n-->\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Simpsons, The}}\n[[Category:The Simpsons| ]]\n[[Category:1989 American television series debuts]]\n[[Category:1980s American animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:1980s American satirical television series]]\n[[Category:1980s American sitcoms]]\n[[Category:1990s American animated comedy television series]]\n[[Category:1990s American satirical television series]]\n[[Category:1990s American sitcoms]]\n[[Category:2000s American ani